The lecture delevered by Steve Jobs had specific audience and purpose we have to noticed. Audiences of the lecture is the Stanford graduated student and their parents, professors and leaders of the university. Most of them had accepted high quality education and weathy. The speaker of the lecture, Steve, is CEO and cofunder of Apple company, also a successful businessman. Speaker compose the lecture to make suggestion to students, which main idea is  they need be modesty in life, and passionate to work.